Ain't no stopping today</i>

25:35.367 --> 25:37.994
<i>If you want something new
Then this is the place</i>

25:38.286 --> 25:40.288
<i>All together, what's next?
Now, we riding the wave</i>

25:40.413 --> 25:41.373
<i>Hey</i>

25:41.540 --> 25:43.583
<i>Get ready, now it's coming</i>

25:43.917 --> 25:46.086
<i>Get ready, now it's coming</i>

25:46.503 --> 25:48.171
<i>Hope you're ready
Now it's coming</i>

25:48.296 --> 25:50.882
<i>Riding on top of the wave</i>

25:50.882 --> 25:52.259
<i>Stand up, this is the place</i>

25:52.259 --> 25:53.426
<i>Are you ready for more?</i>

25:53.552 --> 25:54.928
<i>Next stop, nothing to say</i>

25:55.220 --> 25:57.222
<i>Clap your hands for the new wave
This is the thing</i>

25:57.222 --> 25:58.431
<i>Are you ready for more?</i>

25:58.640 --> 26:00.892
<i>Brand new coming your way
All together now</i>

26:00.892 --> 26:02.644
<i>Stand up, this is the place</i>

26:02.852 --> 26:05.564
<i>Everybody, come on!</i>

26:33.091 --> 26:35.051
- CHUCK Pass the ball.
(ON VIDEO) <i>...handling</i>

26:35.176 --> 26:36.803
<i>- the ball with Meyers on the far side...</i>
- Yep.

26:38.972 --> 26:40.557
Be right back. Must be the food.

26:40.557 --> 26:42.642
<i>Passes it over to Jordan Bell.</i>

26:42.642 --> 26:44.185
<i>- JB goes baseline...</i>
Pizza's here.

26:44.185 --> 26:46.563
<i>...and then dishes it back to Vergeron,</i>

26:46.563 --> 26:50.650
<i>who puts up an easy layup.
What a nice move! And the Lions...</i>

26:50.775 --> 26:53.820
Dad, you have a visitor.
- Who is it?

26:58.116 --> 26:59.117
Hey, Chuck.

27:00.493 --> 27:02.829
<i>You can't have
the darkness without the light.</i>

27:03.288 --> 27:06.666
<i>And you can't bring on the next day
without the night.</i>

27:48.958 --> 27:52.337
Listen, baby, the doctors
are doing everything that they can.

27:54.464 --> 27:56.299
But right now, it doesn't look good.

27:56.299 --> 27:57.384
Wait, no, what?

27:57.676 --> 28:00.720
What... what do you mean, huh?

28:01.930 --> 28:02.972
What do you mean?

28:03.598 --> 28:04.808
I'm sorry, but they...

28:07.102 --> 28:08.228
I'm sorry, baby.

28:11.439 --> 28:14.609
It's gonna be okay. All right?
